{"title_page": "S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 prinia", "text_new": "{{speciesbox\n| name = S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 prinia\n| image = \n| status = LC\n| status_system = IUCN3.1\n| status_ref = <ref name=\"BirdLife International\">{{cite iucn|url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/22713632/0 |title=''Prinia molleri'' |author=BirdLife International |author-link=BirdLife International |year=2012 |access-date=26 November 2013|ref=harv}}</ref>\n| genus = Prinia\n| species = molleri\n| authority = [[Jos\u00e9 Vicente Barbosa du Bocage|Barboza du Bocage]], 1887\n| synonyms = \n}}\n[[File:Prinia molleri MHNT.jpg|thumb|'' Prinia molleri '' - [[MHNT]]]]\n\nThe '''S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 prinia''' (''Prinia molleri'') is a species of bird in the family [[Cisticolidae]].<ref>{{Avibase|843FF0829400704A}}</ref> It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe]] and is found in the island of [[S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 Island|S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9]].<ref name=\"BirdLife International\"/> Its natural [[habitat]]s are subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]] and [[subtropical or tropical moist shrubland]]. The species was named by [[Jos\u00e9 Vicente Barbosa du Bocage]] in 1887.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Commons category}}\n{{Wikispecies}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q2226864}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:prinia, S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9}}\n[[Category:Prinia|S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 prinia]]\n[[Category:Endemic birds of S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe]]\n[[Category:Endemic fauna of S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 Island]]\n[[Category:Birds described in 1887|S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 prinia]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Cisticolidae-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{speciesbox\n| name = S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 prinia\n| image = \n| status = LC\n| status_system = IUCN3.1\n| status_ref = <ref name=\"BirdLife International\">{{cite iucn|url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/22713632/0 |title=''Prinia molleri'' |author=BirdLife International |author-link=BirdLife International |year=2012 |access-date=26 November 2013|ref=harv}}</ref>\n| genus = Prinia\n| species = molleri\n| authority = [[Jos\u00e9 Vicente Barbosa du Bocage|Barboza du Bocage]], 1887\n| synonyms = \n}}\n[[File:Prinia molleri MHNT.jpg|thumb|'' Prinia molleri '' - [[MHNT]]]]\n\nThe '''S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 prinia''' (''Prinia molleri'') is a species of bird in the [[Cisticolidae]] family.<ref>{{Avibase|843FF0829400704A}}</ref> It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe]] and is found in the island of [[S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 Island|S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9]].<ref name=\"BirdLife International\"/> Its natural [[habitat]]s are subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]]s and subtropical or tropical moist [[shrubland]]. The species was named by [[Jos\u00e9 Vicente Barbosa du Bocage]] in 1887.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Commons category}}\n{{Wikispecies}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q2226864}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:prinia, S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9}}\n[[Category:Prinia|S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 prinia]]\n[[Category:Endemic birds of S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe]]\n[[Category:Endemic fauna of S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 Island]]\n[[Category:Birds described in 1887|S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 prinia]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Cisticolidae-stub}}\n", "name_user": "WolfmanSF", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Tom%C3%A9_prinia"}
